 to send rain. Umar would say, \u201cO Allah, we used to ask our Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to supplicate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10928,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/03\/jews-christians-non-muslims-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":18293,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Religion: Fate of Jews, Christians, non-Muslims before Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farisi reported: I asked the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, about the people of religion who had been with me, mentioning their prayers and acts of worship. Then, Allah revealed the verse, \u201cVerily, those who have faith, those who are Jewish, Christian, or Sabians, whoever believed in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7888,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/10\/ummah-multitudes\/","url_meta":{"origin":18293,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: The Prophet sees multitudes of Muslims in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI was shown the nations before me and one or two prophets would pass by with only a few followers, another would pass by with none at all. Then, a large crowd of people passed in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32941,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/28\/expecting-good-allah-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":18293,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Death: Expecting good from Allah at time of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hayyan Abi al-Nadrah reported: I went out to visit Yazid ibn al-Aswad as he was suffering a fatal illness, and I met Wathilah ibn al-Asqa\u2019 who also wanted to visit him. We entered Yazid\u2019s home and Wathilah said, \u201cWhat do you expect from Allah?\u201d Yazid said, \u201cBy Allah, I expect\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2754,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/03\/do-not-exaggerate-status-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":18293,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Do not exaggerate status of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not exaggerate my status\u00a0as the Christians have done with the son of Mary. Verily, I am only a servant, so refer to me as the servant of Allah and His Messenger.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\